-Zašto galamite? -Ja čekam...

145
00:13:02,599 --> 00:13:06,660
Tvoje oči me izluđuju.
-Odlazite odavde!

146
00:13:06,695 --> 00:13:11,085
Moja tufnice.

147
00:13:11,120 --> 00:13:15,832
Jelena Grigorjevna,
oprostite mi, zaboga.

148
00:13:16,705 --> 00:13:24,644
