149
00:13:24,679 --> 00:13:26,994
On ne može bez tebe.

150
00:13:27,029 --> 00:13:30,772
Poljubi me!

151
00:13:31,306 --> 00:13:35,799
Poljubi ga!

152
00:13:38,634 --> 00:13:44,623
